 Issuer: FORTIVE CORP (FTV)\nRoadshow: www.netroadshow.com/nrs/home/#!/?sho
 w=8c1e24e2 | https://netroadshow.com with Entry code: Fortive8246\n\nDeal 
 context:\nFortive Corporation (NYSE: FTV)\, rated Baa1 stable/BBB stable (
 Moody's/S&P)\, has mandated Morgan Stanley\, Barclays\, J.P. Morgan\, and 
 Scotiabank to arrange fixed income investor calls on May 11\, 2026\, ahead
  of a potential senior unsecured notes offering in SEC Registered format. 
 The deal is at the Mandate stage with no size\, tenor\, or pricing informa
 tion disclosed\; an offering may follow subject to market conditions. Morg
 an Stanley is coordinating roadshow logistics\, with three telephonic call
 s scheduled throughout the day and a pre-recorded electronic presentation 
 available via NetRoadshow.
